# XDG global gitignore — applies to every repo on this machine.
# Personal-workflow noise that should never be committed anywhere.

# Worktrees: per the ~/dotfiles/claude/.claude/CLAUDE.md worktree workflow,
# `.worktrees/` lives inside the main repo and holds full sibling worktrees.
# Without this entry, `git status` in the main repo lists every worktree as
# untracked, and gitignore-respecting tools (rg, fd, fzf, telescope) walk into
# the (potentially multi-GB) worktree copies and show duplicate hits.
.worktrees/

# Per-host Claude Code settings — never share machine-specific overrides.
**/.claude/settings.local.json
